Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time known\Nas the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:00:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.28,0:01:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:02:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NWhat the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[explosion]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThat was way off the mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, What's so loud down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Cannon firing practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Awesome! You hit\Nthat thing on the first try!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha think?\NI'm pretty awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,when it comes to aiming!\NAre you impressed yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYeah! You better believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's all settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY] Get out here,\Nya damn pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NMm? That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the hell?\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you guys think that\Nyou can kill my partner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop wrecking our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NLost by a hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] "Famous cook!\NSanji of the Sea Restaurant!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, dearest... 'Fess up.\NWhere are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling. This place is\Ngreat, trust me, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN]\NSo mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not a restaurant in\Nthe middle of the ocean, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY chuckles]\NHere's to your beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY] Just wait\Nuntil you see this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doin'\Nhere, Johnny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Big Bro?! It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NWhy are you on a pirate ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's goin'\Non around here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey relax! Is everything\Nokay? Where's Yosaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[inaudible]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Look. Zoro\Nknows that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[cries] He's been sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NUp until a few days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,he was healthy\Nand full of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He keeps fainting!\NAnd getting really pale!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea\Nwhat's causing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY] His teeth\Nhave been falling out,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and his old wound opened\Nup and started bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He just got worse and worse! I\Ndidn't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:05:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'd just rest on a\Nlittle island. But, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY] A cannonball came\Nflying from this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, USOPP whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, USOPP]\NWe're very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NSorry isn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, USOPP gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NIsn't that right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY] Big Bro. Give it to\Nme straight. Is he gonna die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NSo dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Whatever\Nyou're doing, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mocking his death!\NDammit! You'll--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Luffy! Usopp! We have\Nsome limes in storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!\NBring them here! Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP, LUFFY gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP, LUFFY arguing]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got scurvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NScurvy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NMm-hm. If we weren't too late,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll be just fine\Nin a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY gasps]\NReally, Big Sis?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Don't call me that.\NIt sounds so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm not a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This used to be a hopeless\Ndisease that plagued sailors,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and we just know how\Nto deal with it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY] Here,\N--[USOPP] There you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,--drink up sick guy.\N--have some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] This is caused\Nby a simple deficiency
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of plant-derived\Nnutrients like Vitamin C.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in the old days,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,they couldn't carry fresh\Nfruits and vegetables
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,because they couldn't store\Nthem. We know better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] If a little is\Ngood, a lot is gooder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NYou're gonna be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYou're smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like... a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now. How 'bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--I was right. She isn't dumb.\N--[YOSAKU groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNope. She's smart as a tack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, are morons. Every\Nsailor should know about scurvy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP, LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY, YOSAKU]\NHooray! Hooray! Hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! Hooray! Hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU]\NThe nutrients cured me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NNow you're all better!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't heal\Nthat quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY, YOSAKU]\NAllow us to introduce ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm Yosaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, we're the baddest
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,pirate bounty hunting\Nduo in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY] Big Bro Zoro\Nthere used to be one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU] Glad to make\Nyour acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Small world. I never thought\NI'd see you guys again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY] Well if you think\Nyou're surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU] We never imagined\Nthat the pirate hunter Zoro
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,became a pirate himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NTell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NBig Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Hey... Partner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NLet this be a lesson to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Yeah. This is the\Nkind of trouble you run into
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,when you choose a\Nlife on the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Which means,\Nwhen we're at sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we really gotta think\Nabout how we can get
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the right amount of nutrients\Nwith very little food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's absolutely necessary\Nthat someone on this ship
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,knows how to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NIt's necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! The ship needs a cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI, USOPP]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NLet's go find us a cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in! Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have yummy food,\Neven while we're out at sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:09:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NYou got it. Ha, ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A cook? I know just the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And the food is gonna\Nblow your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!\NLet's go! Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NConsider yourselves warned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is close\Nto the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've heard a lot\Nof rumors lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that a certain hawk-eyed man\Nyou're looking for is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Set a course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,North-Northeast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NAwesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NOur destination is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\N...the sea restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Baratie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, NAMI, USOPP]\NOoooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, heh, what do you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWow. It's a big fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHow lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] This is the\Ncoolest place ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, USOPP cheer]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NJust like I told ya, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[horn blares, bell rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A Marine ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy. They're not gonna\Nstart firing at us, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just my luck! Of course\Nthe marines would show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But. How did that ship...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY] I've never\Nseen that pirate flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you think he\Nknows that you and I
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't a couple of pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[YOSAKU]\NAh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY]\NI am Iron Fist Fullbody!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you can just\Ncall me "Sir"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You there! Who's the\NCaptain?! Identify yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Usopp.\NGot it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We only made our flag\Nthe day before yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right marine!\NAnd I drew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. You did?\NIs that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You two! Right there!\NI've seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that bounty\Nhunter duo that goes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,after the small fish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY] So, you've finally\Nbeen caught by pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Well... Actually we...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY laughs]\NNow that's a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, c'mon baby,\Nlet's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NHey! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You think small time\Nbounty hunters
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,would go after these guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now. Let's go to\Nthat restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY]\NThey're an eyesore. Sink 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NSir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NHe ignored us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time we see him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd better have a little\Nmore respect for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHm. What are these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well those are all wanted\Npirates, Big Sis Nam-- Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, if we defeat\Nthem, we get the reward money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty lucrative business,\Nhuh, Big Sis--?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you guys, look! They're\Npointing a cannon right at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Gum-Gum...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N...Slingshot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK A]\NSir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK B] Are you all\Nright, Head Chef Zeff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK C]\NSir, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY]\NI wonder what that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope our reservation is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK D] Head Chef are\Nyou sure you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NNo! Nothing is "okay"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Never mind, just get back\Nto the restaurant already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but, Sir!\NAren't you, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] You maggots!\NDo you want to see me angry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Feeding the\Ncustomer is a cook's job!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?\NPut me out of business?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK C]\NThis is the guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK D] He's the one\Nresponsible for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NSir, I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams] Your leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NIdiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY]\NHeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Don't worry; you\Ndidn't do this to my leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I see. Good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I'm all banged up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The medical fees
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and repair charges for the\Nship are gonna cost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] I won't ask you\Nto cut me any slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NBut...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm flat broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NMm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well. You're pretty direct, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have money,\Nyou've no choice but to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I wanna make it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll work, unpaid,\Nfor a whole year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! I'll work,\Nunpaid, for a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] I'll let you off\Nthe hook with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh! A year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just say a year?!\NA whole year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP sighs]\NWhat's taking Luffy so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NYeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] They'll probably\Nmake him work without pay
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,for like a whole month.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] He should've just said\Nit was the Marine's fault
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of being so\Nfreakin' honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow. That guy sitting over\Nthere is Lieutenant Fullbody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look kids.\NA big shot from HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow... He's so elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're famous. Everybody\Nin here is looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're wrong.\NThey're all admiring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY]\NMm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This... flavor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And yes... the aroma...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the unmistakable scent
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,from the soil of Micquo\Nof the North Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Bitter with plenty of body,\Nand just a tad sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:17:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This wine... must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the famous Iturutz\NBurger Stein.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me waiter,\Nam I right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh. Not even close, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat up. This dish\Nis best when hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY]\NUh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And, sir. My name's Sanji,\NI'm the Sous Chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All the waiters ran\Noff as of yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATRONS laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN A]\NYou really shouldn't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN A] I can't help it!\NHe looked so confident!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,About wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes... I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems my sense of\Ntaste isn't working today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY] What's going on?!\NI'm certain I requested
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that the owner serve\Nthat particular wine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,when I made this reservation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only work... for one week!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Right.\NA week, get real!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then. Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You wrecked my restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and seriously injured the Head\NChef. That's a serious offense!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just settle that up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,with one or two\Nweeks of unpaid work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYou win! Three weeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...with respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,--[ZEFF yells]\N--[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNo deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited ten long years\Nto become a pirate. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna\Nwaste another year
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,stuck in this restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NMm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get you to let\Nme off the hook in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you value your\Ntime so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what you can do\Nto settle your debt quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya runt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll cost you... a leg, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pricey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Good, I got your attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY]\NTap, tap... Tap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[JOHNNY, YOSAKU]\NHooray! Hooray! Hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY]\NUh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiter! Hey! Get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] I believe I've already\Ntold you, I'm not a waiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What an irresistible\Nbeauty you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you care to join me\Nelsewhere for a glass of wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is "bug soup" on the menu today,\Nor did you make it just for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bug soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. What's this\Nbug doing there, waiter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY] This is gonna ruin\Ntheir restaurant's reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sir. Don't know, really.\NLooks like he's floating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again. It kinda\Nlooks like he's drowning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's hard to say for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATRONS laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY seething]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:21:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you mess\Nwith me! Waiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI, ZORO]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NMm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] You could've eaten it if\Nyou had just taken the bug out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It took three full\Ndays of hard cooking
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to prepare that soup for\Nyou, and you wasted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY] Can't you see\Nthat you're biting off
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,more than you can chew?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the customer here!\NDo you understand me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm paying you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Fullbody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.14,0:21:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.39,0:21:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Fullbody... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Can your money truly\Nsatisfy your hunger?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whadya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI] I'm asking...\NCan it satisfy your hunger?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:21:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:21:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.07,0:22:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're never gonna\Nmake it if you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,just give in sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting] It's still no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.55,0:22:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls] No respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATRONS whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN]\NFullbody?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It-It's Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever waste\Nfood around me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[FULLBODY choking]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At sea, if you ever\Nprovoke your cook,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:22:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you're signing your own\Ndeath warrant. Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.13,0:23:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.76,0:23:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.51,0:23:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.36,0:23:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.59,0:23:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.16,0:23:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.35,0:24:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.31,0:24:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.57,0:24:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.46,0:24:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.02,0:24:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] I wonder if\NLuffy's working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.94,0:24:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] I bet he's just\Ncausing trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Yeah, he doesn't seem\Nlike a productive kinda guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.03,0:24:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.62,0:24:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] What'd you say?!\NThat's not nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.66,0:24:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Hey, have you found\Na cook who'll join us yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.83,0:24:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Yeah! I found him all\Nright! It has to be him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.17,0:24:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.93,0:24:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Unwelcome customer!\NSanji's food and Ghin's debt!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.68,0:24:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be King\Nof the Pirates!

